description: This file defines an immutable data model class 'Booking' used for representing booking information within a mobile application. It includes fields for booking details, a constructor, and methods for serializing to and from JSON.

classes.name: Booking
classes.description: An immutable data class representing a booking, with fields such as id, userId, roomId, status, checkIn, and checkOut, along with JSON serialization methods.

methods.name: fromJson
methods.description: A static factory method that creates a Booking instance from a JSON map.

methods.name: toJson
methods.description: Converts the Booking instance into a JSON map.
